name: Don't go out without your mom
description: That was a beginning of the quarantine in Russia. April 2020. A child walks alone on the melting ice of the Ob River. He does not yet know how far he can be carried on the ice floe. No one knew where that year would take us. The picture was taken on a CANON Zoom prima, Kodak Gold film. The first photo from a series "quarantine". Size 3089x2048.
